'''Traval-Parcor System Institute of Technology''' was a school in the [[Traval-Pacor system/Legends|Traval-Pacor system]].<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

[[Ho'Din/Legends|Ho'Din]] ecologist [[Yansan]] got his degree on Traval-Parcor System Institute of Technology. Although he despised technology, he wanted to learn as much as possible about his "enemy"<ref name="AIR" />

